== Snapshot Packages for Ubuntu ==

There is a snapshot package PPA based on http://emacs.naquadah.org/ available at: https://launchpad.net/~cassou/+archive/emacs

An official emacs-snapshot package is available at https://launchpad.net/~ubuntu-elisp/+archive/ppa

== Fixing Scrollbars ==

Globally

    sudo apt-get purge overlay-scrollbar

To deactivate them only for Emacs use

    LIBOVERLAY_SCROLLBAR=0 emacs


